           -------------------------------------------------
             S H O R T : System Sector Short Communication
           -------------------------------------------------

 Purpose : The System sector short communication feature allows you to
 --------- maintain an online list of short messages which inform the
           other group members on your scheduled work-time.
 How to connect it : if you use the standard ISR@PRIM panel, you
 ------------------- are already connected, otherwise, if you use
    a private ISPF primary panel, you have just to add in the )PROC
    section after the &ZSEL = TRANS ( ... the following line
         SHORT,'CMD(%PAJCSC)'
    which allows the connection.
